            p Developing effective lighting plans to enhance mood and functionality.

          // Service 8: Sustainable Design Solutions
          .service-item
            .section(onclick="showPopup()")
              img(src="assests/img/sustainable_design.jpg" alt="Sustainable Design Solutions")
              h3 Sustainable Design Solutions
            p Incorporating eco-friendly materials and energy-efficient designs.

          // Service 9: Home Staging
          .service-item
            .section(onclick="showPopup()")
              img(src="assests/img/home_staging.jpg" alt="Home Staging")
              h3 Home Staging
            p Preparing homes for sale by enhancing their aesthetic appeal.

          // Service 10: Landscape Design
          .service-item
            .section(onclick="showPopup()")
              img(src="assests/img/landscape_design.jpg" alt="Landscape Design")
              h3 Landscape Design
